{"tid":282198,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[守法撚召喚]規劃署要求還原期限週四屆滿　天水圍泥頭山續改建高球場","createTime":"2017-06-13T07:21:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-13T07:21:07.000Z","uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"71502695ccc8806b7a7c9be5a2746deff9a11bae","tid":282198,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T07:21:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/laii22-01_4BuCn_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Flaii22-01_4BuCn_1200x0.png&h=555e4086&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/hill_dJtJo_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fhill_dJtJo_1200x0.png&h=220bdc11&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n天水圍嘉湖山莊附近的泥頭山，今年一月被揭正被改建成高爾夫球場，規劃署要求將該地段還原的限期將於本週四屆滿，但現時該地段已現高爾夫球場的雛型，舖設了草皮及放置了高球網架、長椅、遮陰帳篷等。元朗區議員李月民質疑當局有意包庇及「放生」泥頭山。<br />\n<br />\n規劃署於今年一月及三月，先後向該地段的擁有人發生強制執行通知書及恢復原狀通知書，要求土地擁有人移走堆放在該地的混凝土，後者的三個月期限將於本月 15 日屆滿。<br />\n<br />\nnow新聞引述一直跟進泥頭山問題的區議員李月民表示，已就問題向不同政府部門反映，但當局回覆稱土地擁有人表示，不知道是誰更改土地用途。李月民批評政府當局執法不力，質疑當局「根本有意放生場主」。<br />\n<br />\n廣告<br />\n元朗地政處回覆傳媒稱，處方發現該私人農地上擺放了帳篷及雜物，但該處為舊契農地，因此不違反地契條款。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/society/%E7%95%B6%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E5%86%87%E5%88%B0-%E8%A6%8F%E5%8A%83%E7%BD%B2%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E9%82%84%E5%8E%9F%E6%9C%9F%E9%99%90%E9%80%B1%E5%9B%9B%E5%B1%86%E6%BB%BF-%E5%A4%A9%E6%B0%B4%E5%9C%8D%E6%B3%A5%E9%A0%AD%E5%B1%B1%E7%BA%8C%E6%94%B9%E5%BB%BA%E9%AB%98%E7%90%83%E5%A0%B4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E7%2595%25B6%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E5%2586%2587%25E5%2588%25B0-%25E8%25A6%258F%25E5%258A%2583%25E7%25BD%25B2%25E8%25A6%2581%25E6%25B1%2582%25E9%2582%2584%25E5%258E%259F%25E6%259C%259F%25E9%2599%2590%25E9%2580%25B1%25E5%259B%259B%25E5%25B1%2586%25E6%25BB%25BF-%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E6%25B0%25B4%25E5%259C%258D%25E6%25B3%25A5%25E9%25A0%25AD%25E5%25B1%25B1%25E7%25BA%258C%25E6%2594%25B9%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E9%25AB%2598%25E7%2590%2583%25E5%25A0%25B4%2F&d=zhzUYjFy93mj2Ai8xmLBgUjIoeaDRyeQRMy%2FzT52C%2Fo%3D&h=a32d328d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E7%2595%25B6%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E5%2586%2587%25E5%2588%25B0-%25E8%25A6%258F%25E5%258A%2583%25E7%25BD%25B2%25E8%25A6%2581%25E6%25B1%2582%25E9%2582%2584%25E5%258E%259F%25E6%259C%259F%25E9%2599%2590%25E9%2580%25B1%25E5%259B%259B%25E5%25B1%2586%25E6%25BB%25BF-%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E6%25B0%25B4%25E5%259C%258D%25E6%25B3%25A5%25E9%25A0%25AD%25E5%25B1%25B1%25E7%25BA%258C%25E6%2594%25B9%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E9%25AB%2598%25E7%2590%2583%25E5%25A0%25B4%2F&h=bbba242f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/society/%E7%95%B6%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E5%86%87%E5%88%B0-%E8%A6%8F%E5%8A%83%E7%BD%B2%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E9%82%84%E5%8E%9F%E6%9C%9F%E9%99%90%E9%80%B1%E5%9B%9B%E5%B1%86%E6%BB%BF-%E5%A4%A9%E6%B0%B4%E5%9C%8D%E6%B3%A5%E9%A0%AD%E5%B1%B1%E7%BA%8C%E6%94%B9%E5%BB%BA%E9%AB%98%E7%90%83%E5%A0%B4/</a>"}]}